| ------- | ------------- | ---------------- |
| e2e-resource-exhaustion | `optimization/` | `version` |
| experiment-dataset-triage | `evaluation/` | `version` |
| batch-subprocess-signal-hang | `debugging/` | `version` |
| tensor-dtype-native-ops-inversion | `architecture/` | (none) |

### Detection Commands

```bash
